node.text: Behind social media it’s Corey, Most kind hearted nigga you’ll ever meet 💯 Most realist you’ll meet. This weekend was something I’ve been waiting on for 3 years. I finally done achieved getting my family out here it was all done separate ways because of their schedules but man just seeing my family happy bring tears to my eyes 🙏🏽 It was so real we didn’t even take one picture together because we was too busy enjoying the time. God is Good and I’m so happy 💯🙏🏽 No one can take what I do for others away from me I’ll always walk with God 👨🏽‍🦯
